{"tid":1943434,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"牛市之美國3個月國債跌至負利率，代表乜？","createTime":"2020-03-25T16:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T00:46:01.000Z","uid":40478,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af39d4c850197b4e3ea10e17bdcc084e6d458282","tid":1943434,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/25/negative-rates-come-to-the-us-1-month-and-3-month-treasury-bill-yields-are-now-negative.html?__source=iosappshare%7Ccom.apple.UIKit.activity.CopyToPasteboard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F03%2F25%2Fnegative-rates-come-to-the-us-1-month-and-3-month-treasury-bill-yields-are-now-negative.html%3F__source%3Diosappshare%257Ccom.apple.UIKit.activity.CopyToPasteboard&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4T2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=85d981d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/25/negative-rates-come-to-the-us-1-month-and-3-month-treasury-bill-yields-are-now-negative.html?__source=iosappshare%7Ccom.apple.UIKit.activity.CopyToPasteboard</a><br />\n<br />\n話說無論邊個國家都好，總之古時候，擺錢係「銀行」（果時係由金匠、寺廟、聖殿騎士之類既人物經營）係要付費既，用現代語言講，就係負利率。擺錢係銀行而銀行竟然反而比番息你，其實係一個非常晚期既現象。<br />\n<br />\n點解呢？因為古時治安唔好，擺錢係屋企比人偷比人搶既機會大，比少少保護費將錢擺係信用好武力強既人物手上，係值得做既。直至社會發展到大家認為政府強到足夠保護大家，以至唔肯交保護費，有膽放錢係屋企，先有正利率既出現黎吸引儲戶<br />\n<br />\n負利率就係交保險費既概念，呢家市場上有一班人認為最少係三個月，交少少保護費比美帝求保護係值得既，點解佢地寧願蝕少少都唔肯擺錢係銀行呢？佢地預視緊金融系統有大風險，驚擺錢係銀行銀行汁撚左血本無歸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da91b0ba1b577cdc2810451c8ffbd2db4b8442e","tid":1943434,"uid":31298,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"柒到仆街呢啲解釋 有讀過下書都想笑鳩你"},{"pid":"f3bc010234514983000996488edb6fc584d2a8d9","tid":1943434,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:03:54.000Z","msg":"日本都試過負利率"},{"pid":"92d4e271b6a1a382afec742eca8fcac9d5d8b7d6","tid":1943434,"uid":6974,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score"